To run all simulation tests, invoke

    ./tests_modelsim.sh

You can specify the PLB bus version and corresponding OSIF (plb_osif or
xps_osif) to simulate by setting the PLB_VER environment variable, e.g.:

    PLB_VER=34 ./tests_modelsim.sh

or
    PLB_VER=46 ./tests_modelsim.sh

If you don't set the PLB_VER variable, the most recent PLB bus version that
ReconOS supports is used.

